                    Dimension Films(2007). Length : 95min                     


 After an experimental bio nerve gas is accidentally released at a remote     
 U.S. military base in Texas, those exposed to the gas turn into              
 flesh-eating, mutating zombies out to kill. An assortment of various people  
 who include stripper Cherry (Rose McGowen), her shady mechanic ex-boyfriend  
 Wray (Freddy Rodriguez), a strong-willed doctor (Marley Shelton), the local  
 sheriff, and an assortment of various people must join forces to survive     
 the night as the so-called "sickos" threaten to take over the whole town     
 and the world.
